sallocation-in-history-7d44aa4b?mod=dist_amp_social&amp;link=sfmw_tw\">In an analysis of the crazy spending on AI infrastructure</a><span>, MarketWatch just quoted a </span><a href=\"https://x.com/garymarcus/status/2049612941419565456?s=61\">tweet</a><span> from yours truly:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1622,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:460933,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/196043904?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260430210253_2003667d-bfa7-4592-82d6-62f45826e921_1477x1645.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p><span>The very fact that my warnings, technical and economic, are at long last starting to break through (</span><em><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ykvf3MunGf8\">Last Week Tonight</a></em><span> on Sunday, MarketWatch today, and so on) is a strong sign that times are changing, and that skepticism is rising.</span></p>\n   <p>As it should.</p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为，今年可能达到 7000 亿美元的 AI 基础设施巨额支出，是历史上最大的资本错配，其驱动力是炒作而非现实的技术与经济回报。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gary Marcus 认为，今年可能达到 7000 亿美元的 AI 基础设施巨额支出，是历史上最大的资本错配，其驱动力是炒作而非现实的技术与经济回报。",
  "summary": "著名 AI 批评家 Gary Marcus 认为，当前对 AI 基础设施的巨额投资（今年可能达到 7000 亿美元）是历史上最大的资本错配。他指出，自己长期以来在技术和经济方面的警告，如今在 MarketWatch 和 Last Week Tonight 等主流媒体上获得了关注，这证明怀疑情绪终于开始抬头。文章认为，炒作周期导致了非理性的繁荣，企业将巨额资金投入基础设施，但鉴于当前 AI 技术的局限性，这些投入可能无法带来相应的回报。Marcus 的核心论点是，这场支出狂潮不可持续，并且很可能导致一次重大调整，因为 AI 所承诺的回报无法达到预期的规模。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "大规模的 AI 基础设施支出是一次历史性的资本错配。",
      "explanation": "Gary Marcus 认为，今年预计高达 7000 亿美元的 AI 支出是由炒作而非实际回报驱动的，这代表了一次重大的资本错配。"
    },
    {
      "point": "对 AI 经济可行性的怀疑情绪正在增长。",
      "explanation": "Marcus 指出，他长期以来的警告如今正被 MarketWatch 和 Last Week Tonight 等主流媒体所呼应，这表明市场情绪正在转变。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 炒作周期正导致不可持续的投资。",
      "explanation": "文章认为，当前的支出狂潮是非理性的，因为 AI 所承诺的回报不太可能达到预期的规模，这可能导致市场调整。"
    }
  ],
